<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q8_v1" title="Q8_v1" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration><qti-item-body>
    <p>
      Se tiene la siguiente ficha de preparación del batido:<br />
      • Cantidad de vasos de batido a preparar: 
      <m:math><m:mn>160</m:mn></m:math>.<br />
      • Ingredientes por vaso:<br />
        • 
      <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>
      taza de leche de coco.<br />
        • 
      <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>
      de taza de pulpa de mango.<br />
      • Equivalencia de medida: 
      <m:math><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:math>
      taza = 
      <m:math><m:mn>250</m:mn></m:math>
      mL.
    </p>
    <p>
      ¿Cuántos mL de leche de coco se necesitan en total para preparar todos los vasos de batido?
    </p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="true" max-choices="1">
      <qti-prompt>Elige una alternativa.</qti-prompt>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA"><m:math><m:mn>10&#160;000</m:mn></m:math> mL<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Cada vaso usa 1/2 taza de leche de coco, es decir, 125 mL porque <m:math><m:mn>250</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>125</m:mn></m:math>. Para 160 vasos se necesita <m:math><m:mn>160</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>125</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>20&#160;000</m:mn></m:math> mL. Por lo tanto, <m:math><m:mn>10&#160;000</m:mn></m:math> mL no alcanza.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB"><m:math><m:mn>20&#160;000</m:mn></m:math> mL<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Cada vaso requiere 1/2 taza de leche de coco. Como 1 taza = 250 mL, entonces 1/2 taza = 125 mL. Para 160 vasos: <m:math><m:mn>160</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>125</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>20&#160;000</m:mn></m:math> mL. Por eso se necesitan <m:math><m:mn>20&#160;000</m:mn></m:math> mL en total.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC"><m:math><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn></m:math> mL<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. La leche de coco por vaso es 1/2 taza, no más. Como 1 taza = 250 mL, entonces 1/2 taza = 125 mL. Para 160 vasos: <m:math><m:mn>160</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>125</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>20&#160;000</m:mn></m:math> mL. Por lo tanto, <m:math><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn></m:math> mL es mayor que la cantidad necesaria.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD"><m:math><m:mn>40&#160;000</m:mn></m:math> mL<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si se usaran <m:math><m:mn>40&#160;000</m:mn></m:math> mL para 160 vasos, eso correspondería a <m:math><m:mn>40&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>160</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>250</m:mn></m:math> mL por vaso, o sea, 1 taza por vaso. Pero el enunciado indica 1/2 taza por vaso, que equivale a 125 mL. La cantidad correcta es <m:math><m:mn>160</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>125</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>20&#160;000</m:mn></m:math> mL.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Identificar la cantidad de leche de coco por vaso</strong></p>
            <p>Cada vaso lleva</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mfrac>
                  <m:mn>1</m:mn>
                  <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                </m:mfrac>
              </m:math>
              taza de leche de coco.
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Convertir esa cantidad a mL</strong></p>
            <p>El enunciado indica que</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mn>1</m:mn>
              </m:math>
              taza =
              <m:math>
                <m:mn>250</m:mn>
              </m:math>
              mL.
            </p>
            <p>Entonces,</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mfrac>
                  <m:mn>1</m:mn>
                  <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                </m:mfrac>
                <m:mo>×</m:mo>
                <m:mn>250</m:mn>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mn>125</m:mn>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Cada vaso necesita 125 mL de leche de coco.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Multiplicar por la cantidad total de vasos</strong></p>
            <p>Se preparan 160 vasos, por lo tanto:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mn>160</m:mn>
                <m:mo>×</m:mo>
                <m:mn>125</m:mn>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mn>20&#160;000</m:mn>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Concluir</strong></p>
            <p>Se necesitan <m:math><m:mn>20&#160;000</m:mn></m:math> mL de leche de coco para preparar todos los vasos de batido.</p>
            <p>La alternativa correcta es la <strong>B</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>